verses.pali:
Manopubbaṅgamā dhammā, manoseṭṭhā manomayā;
Manasā ce paduṭṭhena, bhāsati vā karoti vā;
Tato naṁ dukkhamanveti, cakkaṁva vahato padaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Manopubbangama dhamma, manosettha manomaya;
Manasa ce padutthena, bhasati va karoti va;
Tato nam dukkhamanveti, cakkamva vahato padam.

verses.pali:
Manopubbaṅgamā dhammā, manoseṭṭhā manomayā;
Manasā ce pasannena, bhāsati vā karoti vā;
Tato naṁ sukhamanveti, chāyāva anapāyinī.

verses.transliteration:
Manopubbangama dhamma, manosettha manomaya;
Manasa ce pasannena, bhasati va karoti va;
Tato nam sukhamanveti, chayava anapayini.

verses.pali:
Subhānupassiṁ viharantaṁ, indriyesu asaṁvutaṁ;
Bhojanamhi cāmattaññuṁ, kusītaṁ hīnavīriyaṁ;
Taṁ ve pasahati māro, vāto rukkhaṁva dubbalaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Subhanupassim viharantam, indriyesu asamvutam;
Bhojanamhi camattannum, kusitam hinaviriyam;
Tam ve pasahati maro, vato rukkhamva dubbalam.

verses.pali:
Asubhānupassiṁ viharantaṁ, Indriyesu susaṁvutaṁ;
Bhojanamhi ca mattaññuṁ, Saddhaṁ āraddhavīriyaṁ;
Taṁ ve nappasahati māro, Vāto selaṁva pabbataṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Asubhanupassim viharantam, Indriyesu susamvutam;
Bhojanamhi ca mattannum, Saddham araddhaviriyam;
Tam ve nappasahati maro, Vato selamva pabbatam.

verses.pali:
Appampi ce saṁhita bhāsamāno, Dhammassa hoti anudhammacārī;
Rāgañca dosañca pahāya mohaṁ, Sammappajāno suvimuttacitto;
Anupādiyāno idha vā huraṁ vā, Sa bhāgavā sāmaññassa hoti. Yamakavaggo paṭhamo.

verses.transliteration:
Appampi ce samhita bhasamano, Dhammassa hoti anudhammacari;
Raganca dosanca pahaya moham, Sammappajano suvimuttacitto;
Anupadiyano idha va huram va, Sa bhagava samannassa hoti. Yamakavaggo pathamo.

verses.pali:
Pamādaṁ appamādena, yadā nudati paṇḍito;
Paññāpāsādamāruyha, asoko sokiniṁ pajaṁ;
Pabbataṭṭhova bhūmaṭṭhe, dhīro bāle avekkhati.

verses.transliteration:
Pamadam appamadena, yada nudati pandito;
Pannapasadamaruyha, asoko sokinim pajam;
Pabbatatthova bhumatthe, dhiro bale avekkhati.

verses.pali:
Mameva kata maññantu, gihī pabbajitā ubho;
Mamevātivasā assu, kiccākiccesu kismici;
Iti bālassa saṅkappo, icchā māno ca vaḍḍhati.

verses.transliteration:
Mameva kata mannantu, gihi pabbajita ubho;
Mamevativasa assu, kiccakiccesu kismici;
Iti balassa sankappo, iccha mano ca vaddhati.

verses.pali:
Aññā hi lābhūpanisā, aññā nibbānagāminī;
Evametaṁ abhiññāya, bhikkhu buddhassa sāvako;
Sakkāraṁ nābhinandeyya, vivekamanubrūhaye. Bālavaggo pañcamo.

verses.transliteration:
Anna hi labhupanisa, anna nibbanagamini;
Evametam abhinnaya, bhikkhu buddhassa savako;
Sakkaram nabhinandeyya, vivekamanubruhaye. Balavaggo pancamo.

verses.pali:
Nidhīnaṁva pavattāraṁ, yaṁ passe vajjadassinaṁ;
Niggayhavādiṁ medhāviṁ, tādisaṁ paṇḍitaṁ bhaje;
Tādisaṁ bhajamānassa, seyyo hoti na pāpiyo.

verses.transliteration:
Nidhinamva pavattaram, yam passe vajjadassinam;
Niggayhavadim medhavim, tadisam panditam bhaje;
Tadisam bhajamanassa, seyyo hoti na papiyo.

verses.pali:
Yesaṁ sambodhiyaṅgesu, sammā cittaṁ subhāvitaṁ;
Ādānapaṭinissagge, anupādāya ye ratā;
Khīṇāsavā jutimanto, te loke parinibbutā. Paṇḍitavaggo chaṭṭho.

verses.transliteration:
Yesam sambodhiyangesu, samma cittam subhavitam;
Adanapatinissagge, anupadaya ye rata;
Khinasava jutimanto, te loke parinibbuta. Panditavaggo chattho.

verses.pali:
Yesaṁ sannicayo natthi, ye pariññātabhojanā;
Suññato animitto ca, vimokkho yesaṁ gocaro;
Ākāseva sakuntānaṁ, gati tesaṁ durannayā.

verses.transliteration:
Yesam sannicayo natthi, ye parinnatabhojana;
Sunnato animitto ca, vimokkho yesam gocaro;
Akaseva sakuntanam, gati tesam durannaya.

verses.pali:
Yassāsavā parikkhīṇā, āhāre ca anissito;
Suññato animitto ca, vimokkho yassa gocaro;
Ākāseva sakuntānaṁ, padaṁ tassa durannayaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Yassasava parikkhina, ahare ca anissito;
Sunnato animitto ca, vimokkho yassa gocaro;
Akaseva sakuntanam, padam tassa durannayam.

verses.pali:
Māse māse sahassena, yo yajetha sataṁ samaṁ;
Ekañca bhāvitattānaṁ, muhuttamapi pūjaye;
Sāyeva pūjanā seyyo, yañce vassasataṁ hutaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Mase mase sahassena, yo yajetha satam samam;
Ekanca bhavitattanam, muhuttamapi pujaye;
Sayeva pujana seyyo, yance vassasatam hutam.

verses.pali:
Yo ca vassasataṁ jantu, aggiṁ paricare vane;
Ekañca bhāvitattānaṁ, muhuttamapi pūjaye;
Sāyeva pūjanā seyyo, yañce vassasataṁ hutaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Yo ca vassasatam jantu, aggim paricare vane;
Ekanca bhavitattanam, muhuttamapi pujaye;
Sayeva pujana seyyo, yance vassasatam hutam.

verses.pali:
Māvamaññetha pāpassa, na mantaṁ āgamissati;
Udabindunipātena, udakumbhopi pūrati;
Bālo pūrati pāpassa, thokaṁ thokampi ācinaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Mavamannetha papassa, na mantam agamissati;
Udabindunipatena, udakumbhopi purati;
Balo purati papassa, thokam thokampi acinam.

verses.pali:
Māvamaññetha puññassa, na mandaṁ āgamissati;
Udabindunipātena, udakumbhopi pūrati;
Dhīro pūrati puññassa, thokaṁ thokampi ācinaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Mavamannetha punnassa, na mandam agamissati;
Udabindunipatena, udakumbhopi purati;
Dhiro purati punnassa, thokam thokampi acinam.

verses.pali:
Asso yathā bhadro kasāniviṭṭho, Ātāpino saṁvegino bhavātha;
Saddhāya sīlena ca vīriyena ca, Samādhinā dhammavinicchayena ca;
Sampannavijjācaraṇā patissatā, Jahissatha dukkhamidaṁ anappakaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Asso yatha bhadro kasanivittho, Atapino samvegino bhavatha;
Saddhaya silena ca viriyena ca, Samadhina dhammavinicchayena ca;
Sampannavijjacarana patissata, Jahissatha dukkhamidam anappakam.

verses.pali:
Gahakāraka diṭṭhosi, puna gehaṁ na kāhasi;
Sabbā te phāsukā bhaggā, gahakūṭaṁ visaṅkhataṁ;
Visaṅkhāragataṁ cittaṁ, taṇhānaṁ khayamajjhagā.

verses.transliteration:
Gahakaraka ditthosi, puna geham na kahasi;
Sabba te phasuka bhagga, gahakutam visankhatam;
Visankharagatam cittam, tanhanam khayamajjhaga.

verses.pali:
Yo sāsanaṁ arahataṁ, ariyānaṁ dhammajīvinaṁ;
Paṭikkosati dummedho, diṭṭhiṁ nissāya pāpikaṁ;
Phalāni kaṭṭhakasseva, attaghātāya phallati.

verses.transliteration:
Yo sasanam arahatam, ariyanam dhammajivinam;
Patikkosati dummedho, ditthim nissaya papikam;
Phalani katthakasseva, attaghataya phallati.

verses.pali:
Attanā hi kataṁ pāpaṁ, attanā saṅkilissati;
Attanā akataṁ pāpaṁ, attanāva visujjhati;
Suddhī asuddhi paccattaṁ, nāñño aññaṁ visodhaye.

verses.transliteration:
Attana hi katam papam, attana sankilissati;
Attana akatam papam, attanava visujjhati;
Suddhi asuddhi paccattam, nanno annam visodhaye.

verses.pali:
Anūpavādo anūpaghāto, Pātimokkhe ca saṁvaro;
Mattaññutā ca bhattasmiṁ, Pantañca sayanāsanaṁ;
Adhicitte ca āyogo, Etaṁ buddhāna sāsanaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Anupavado anupaghato, Patimokkhe ca samvaro;
Mattannuta ca bhattasmim, Pantanca sayanasanam;
Adhicitte ca ayogo, Etam buddhana sasanam.

verses.pali:
Bālasaṅgatacārī hi, dīghamaddhāna socati;
Dukkho bālehi saṁvāso, amitteneva sabbadā;
Dhīro ca sukhasaṁvāso, ñātīnaṁva samāgamo.

verses.transliteration:
Balasangatacari hi, dighamaddhana socati;
Dukkho balehi samvaso, amitteneva sabbada;
Dhiro ca sukhasamvaso, natinamva samagamo.

verses.pali:
Porāṇametaṁ atula, netaṁ ajjatanāmiva;
Nindanti tuṇhimāsīnaṁ, nindanti bahubhāṇinaṁ;
Mitabhāṇimpi nindanti, natthi loke anindito.

verses.transliteration:
Poranametam atula, netam ajjatanamiva;
Nindanti tunhimasinam, nindanti bahubhaninam;
Mitabhanimpi nindanti, natthi loke anindito.

verses.pali:
Dadāti ve yathāsaddhaṁ, yathāpasādanaṁ jano;
Tattha yo ca maṅku bhavati, paresaṁ pānabhojane;
Na so divā vā rattiṁ vā, samādhimadhigacchati.

verses.transliteration:
Dadati ve yathasaddham, yathapasadanam jano;
Tattha yo ca manku bhavati, paresam panabhojane;
Na so diva va rattim va, samadhimadhigacchati.

verses.pali:
Sudassaṁ vajjamaññesaṁ, attano pana duddasaṁ;
Paresaṁ hi so vajjāni, opunāti yathā bhusaṁ;
Attano pana chādeti, kaliṁva kitavā saṭho.

verses.transliteration:
Sudassam vajjamannesam, attano pana duddasam;
Paresam hi so vajjani, opunati yatha bhusam;
Attano pana chadeti, kalimva kitava satho.

verses.pali:
Na tāvatā dhammadharo, yāvatā bahu bhāsati;
Yo ca appampi sutvāna, dhammaṁ kāyena passati;
Sa ve dhammadharo hoti, yo dhammaṁ nappamajjati.

verses.transliteration:
Na tavata dhammadharo, yavata bahu bhasati;
Yo ca appampi sutvana, dhammam kayena passati;
Sa ve dhammadharo hoti, yo dhammam nappamajjati.

verses.pali:
Yogā ve jāyatī bhūri, ayogā bhūrisaṅkhayo;
Etaṁ dvedhāpathaṁ ñatvā, bhavāya vibhavāya ca;
Tathāttānaṁ niveseyya, yathā bhūri pavaḍḍhati.

verses.transliteration:
Yoga ve jayati bhuri, ayoga bhurisankhayo;
Etam dvedhapatham natva, bhavaya vibhavaya ca;
Tathattanam niveseyya, yatha bhuri pavaddhati.

verses.pali:
Yesañca susamāraddhā, niccaṁ kāyagatā sati;
Akiccaṁ te na sevanti, kicce sātaccakārino;
Satānaṁ sampajānānaṁ, atthaṁ gacchanti āsavā.

verses.transliteration:
Yesanca susamaraddha, niccam kayagata sati;
Akiccam te na sevanti, kicce sataccakarino;
Satanam sampajananam, attham gacchanti asava.

verses.pali:
Duppabbajjaṁ durabhiramaṁ, Durāvāsā gharā dukhā;
Dukkhosamānasaṁvāso, Dukkhānupatitaddhagū;
Tasmā na caddhagū siyā, Na ca dukkhānupatito siyā.

verses.transliteration:
Duppabbajjam durabhiramam, Duravasa ghara dukha;
Dukkhosamanasamvaso, Dukkhanupatitaddhagu;
Tasma na caddhagu siya, Na ca dukkhanupatito siya.

verses.pali:
Nagaraṁ yathā paccantaṁ, guttaṁ santarabāhiraṁ;
Evaṁ gopetha attānaṁ, khaṇo vo mā upaccagā;
Khaṇātītā hi socanti, nirayamhi samappitā.

verses.transliteration:
Nagaram yatha paccantam, guttam santarabahiram;
Evam gopetha attanam, khano vo ma upaccaga;
Khanatita hi socanti, nirayamhi samappita.

verses.pali:
Taṁ vo vadāmi bhaddaṁ vo, yāvantettha samāgatā;
Taṇhāya mūlaṁ khaṇatha, usīratthova bīraṇaṁ;
Mā vo naḷaṁva sotova, māro bhañji punappunaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Tam vo vadami bhaddam vo, yavantettha samagata;
Tanhaya mulam khanatha, usiratthova biranam;
Ma vo nalamva sotova, maro bhanji punappunam.

verses.pali:
Vītataṇho anādāno, Niruttipadakovido;
Akkharānaṁ sannipātaṁ, Jaññā pubbāparāni ca;
Sa ve “antimasārīro, Mahāpañño mahāpuriso”ti vuccati.

verses.transliteration:
Vitatanho anadano, Niruttipadakovido;
Akkharanam sannipatam, Janna pubbaparani ca;
Sa ve “antimasariro, Mahapanno mahapuriso”ti vuccati.

verses.pali:
Kāyena saṁvaro sādhu, sādhu vācāya saṁvaro;
Manasā saṁvaro sādhu, sādhu sabbattha saṁvaro;
Sabbattha saṁvuto bhikkhu, sabbadukkhā pamuccati.

verses.transliteration:
Kayena samvaro sadhu, sadhu vacaya samvaro;
Manasa samvaro sadhu, sadhu sabbattha samvaro;
Sabbattha samvuto bhikkhu, sabbadukkha pamuccati.

verses.pali:
Mitte bhajassu kalyāṇe, suddhājīve atandite;
Paṭisanthāravutyassa, ācārakusalo siyā;
Tato pāmojjabahulo, dukkhassantaṁ karissati.

verses.transliteration:
Mitte bhajassu kalyane, suddhajive atandite;
Patisantharavutyassa, acarakusalo siya;
Tato pamojjabahulo, dukkhassantam karissati.

verses.pali:
Attā hi attano nātho, ko hi nātho paro siyā;
Attā hi attano gati, tasmā saṁyamamattānaṁ;
Assaṁ bhadraṁva vāṇijo.

verses.transliteration:
Atta hi attano natho, ko hi natho paro siya;
Atta hi attano gati, tasma samyamamattanam;
Assam bhadramva vanijo.

verses.pali:
Divā tapati ādicco, rattimābhāti candimā;
Sannaddho khattiyo tapati, jhāyī tapati brāhmaṇo;
Atha sabbamahorattiṁ, buddho tapati tejasā.

verses.transliteration:
Diva tapati adicco, rattimabhati candima;
Sannaddho khattiyo tapati, jhayi tapati brahmano;
Atha sabbamahorattim, buddho tapati tejasa.

verses.pali:
Na cāhaṁ brāhmaṇaṁ brūmi, yonijaṁ mattisambhavaṁ;
Bhovādi nāma so hoti, sace hoti sakiñcano;
Akiñcanaṁ anādānaṁ, tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Na caham brahmanam brumi, yonijam mattisambhavam;
Bhovadi nama so hoti, sace hoti sakincano;
Akincanam anadanam, tamaham brumi brahmanam.

verses.pali:
Yomaṁ palipathaṁ duggaṁ, saṁsāraṁ mohamaccagā;
Tiṇṇo pāraṅgato jhāyī, anejo akathaṅkathī;
Anupādāya nibbuto, tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Yomam palipatham duggam, samsaram mohamaccaga;
Tinno parangato jhayi, anejo akathankathi;
Anupadaya nibbuto, tamaham brumi brahmanam.

verses.pali:
Yodha taṇhaṁ pahantvāna, anāgāro paribbaje;
Taṇhābhavaparikkhīṇaṁ, tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ. Jotikattheravatthu Yodha taṇhaṁ pahantvāna, anāgāro paribbaje;
Taṇhābhavaparikkhīṇaṁ, tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Yodha tanham pahantvana, anagaro paribbaje;
Tanhabhavaparikkhinam, tamaham brumi brahmanam. Jotikattheravatthu Yodha tanham pahantvana, anagaro paribbaje;
Tanhabhavaparikkhinam, tamaham brumi brahmanam.

verses.pali:
Pubbenivāsaṁ yo vedi, saggāpāyañca passati;
Atho jātikkhayaṁ patto, abhiññāvosito muni;
Sabbavositavosānaṁ, tamahaṁ brūmi brāhmaṇaṁ.

verses.transliteration:
Pubbenivasam yo vedi, saggapayanca passati;
Atho jatikkhayam patto, abhinnavosito muni;
Sabbavositavosanam, tamaham brumi brahmanam.
